{"tid":960890,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】習近平與特朗普通電　稱貿易協商取得良好進展","createTime":"2018-12-29T17:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T16:10:04.000Z","uid":66271,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"942fd59fc80f1a38a13198fc00d288eddac43d0e","tid":960890,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T17:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2265855/org/78e2724d09b98a61a74789334479b62d.jpg/wZsR0A2KUwFY5PPzCMDnVfNgTSn2wE5I4zUhpuM1IaY?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2265855%2Forg%2F78e2724d09b98a61a74789334479b62d.jpg%2FwZsR0A2KUwFY5PPzCMDnVfNgTSn2wE5I4zUhpuM1IaY%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=dd4036ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平上周六（29日）與美國總統特朗普通電話。特朗普表示，十分重視與習近平的關係，強調兩國關係非常重要，很高興兩國的工作團隊正努力就雙方對話協商努力推進。<br />\n<br />\n雙方形容在中美貿易問題上，正取得積極進展，期望能早日達成協議，特朗普表示，若能達成協議，將會涵蓋所有議題、領域和爭議。兩人也就朝鮮半島半島局勢及地區安全問題交換意見，習近平重申，中方鼓勵和支持朝美雙方繼續開展對話並取得積極成果。<br />\n<br />\n習近平強調，中美兩國關係正處於重要階段，兩國工作團隊正在積極推進落實工作，希望雙方團隊相向而行抓緊工作，爭取盡早達成既互利雙贏、又對世界有利的協議。"},{"pid":"f04ced32109ff6cc867a149f0b4011d0a664281d","tid":960890,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T17:26:07.000Z","msg":"牛三<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09c0542a308d6d9c2a6cd6af7f29f124e54e58b","tid":960890,"uid":106634,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T17:26:09.000Z","msg":"睇嚟侵侵就快又嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad384c7926d12804256bf3b16c7014d49467fbfc","tid":960890,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c09c0542a308d6d9c2a6cd6af7f29f124e54e58b","tid":960890,"uid":106634,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T17:26:09.000Z","msg":"睇嚟侵侵就快又嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as